PRAYERS and messages of love and support have been pouring in for sick gospel singer Lundi Tyamara.Mzansi people are giving support to Lundi&rsquo;s family and friends as he fights for his life at Edenvale Hospital in Ekurhuleni.His friends and colleagues came together and hosted a Prayer 4 Lundi session tonight in the Joburg CBD. The session was open to colleagues, friends, fans and members of the community.